{
  "stem": "19923.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And every once in a while, the train would stop somewhere in the country and peasants and farmers and neighboring people would come to the train and bring food and water for the people.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "That's how we were able to survive.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The only thing we had for bedding was straw.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We slept on the straw.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And there were at least 30, 40 people in each box car for-- for three days.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And while we was zigzagging around France trying to locate a place where we could safely end up, we also went through Amiens, which is not far from Paris, and I remember this from what people have told me.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And in the middle of the night, we watched the bombardment-- the German bombardment of Paris.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I still have vivid recollections of waking up and seeing-- and seeing-- seeing air balloons that the French used to stop the dive bombers and saw flashes of light from the fire that-- both from the planes coming down and the flashes of light from the anti-aircraft guns shooting up at the planes.",
      "word_count": 54
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And for a nine-year-old boy, it was quite a war experience to see the actual fighting while it was going on.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And this was also-- the train had stopped because it couldn't go any further while all the bombardment was going on.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But I remember that was Amiens.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And then from then we continued on and after three days, we wound up in the-- in the south, near-- not far from Toulouse.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Tolouse is T-O-U-L-O-U-S-E.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "That's in southern France.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "It's a large city in southern France.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And about 35 miles south of there is a city called Villefranche.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Villefranche is V-I-L-L-E-F-R-A-N-C-H-E.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was a little tiny village and this is where we wound up.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
